\f6 multiworld_notification_level
\f1 \'94 in 
\f6 application_settings.json
\f1  to one of \'93none\'94, \'93normal\'94 (default), or \'93verbose\'94 (the old behavior).\
The extension now allows wss:// service URIs for multiworld servers.\
Note: I have received reports of compatibility issues with the latest multiworld server changes, but it is not clear that there are not basic code issues in that release. These will be resolved in a subsequent update, once things have stabilized.\
